    "text": [
        "Dear Sir or Madam,",
        "I am writing to you with a great complaint about a mistake that your telephone company did to me. This never happened before and I am very upset about the whole situation.",
        "My bill for the last month never came, regardless of me paying it as soon as it was calculated. Firstly, I thought the post is late, but after waiting a whole month, I received another bill where it said that I have to pay for the last two months of my telephone bill. Additionally, my telephone services have been shut down and now, I can not call anyone because of your mistake.",
        "I always paid my bills on time, and this happens for the first time. I attached invoice photos as proof of me paying the last month's bill.",
        "I urge you to find a solution and renew my old services or I will change my phone company next week.",
        "Yours faithfully,",
        "Ognjen Rankovic"
    ],
